quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  17,100,"Say (to the disbelievers): "
  17,101,"And indeed We gave Mûsâ (Moses) nine clear signs. Ask then the Children of Israel, when he came to them, then Fir‘aun (Pharaoh) said to him: "
  17,102,"[Mûsâ (Moses)] said: "
