  19,28,"",footnotes:1:{19:28} This Hârûn (Aaron) is not the brother of Mûsâ (Moses), but he was another pious man at the time of Maryam (Mary).
  19,29,"Then she pointed to him. They said: ",footnotes:1:{19:29} See the footnote of (Verse 3:46).
